{"tid":2198262,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"科學方法有咩咁巴閉","createTime":"2020-09-11T08:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T06:07:28.000Z","uid":88663,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"abb690f1505b06d3d10028cd16d656af3bd585e3","tid":2198262,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:28:06.000Z","msg":"中醫係垃圾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/139369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/139369</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n，無聊search到呢個post，見到裏面好多巴絲對「科學方法」呢個詞嘅意思有誤解"},{"pid":"7964db71a296edf1d17819c0ac18ecfcb339147d","tid":2198262,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:29:08.000Z","msg":"我就想藉此post分享一下科學方法嘅真正意思<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fd-V_37QhXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ffd-V_37QhXc&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=947c04c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fd-V_37QhXc</a><br />\n何謂科學方法？科學方法是否最科學？"},{"pid":"6bdde7572198dff502a60497d7a490c35e72464d","tid":2198262,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:31:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xAHtQKCpU1A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxAHtQKCpU1A&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=97adc5af\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xAHtQKCpU1A</a><br />\n奧坎的剃刀，科學方法的利器"},{"pid":"14894509cefd560ed907a5630815eadee15559bc","tid":2198262,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:44:36.000Z","msg":"唔得閒睇片<br />\n樓主可唔可以簡單總結吓"},{"pid":"12123db5e6f12a58a5dcec84525e3adf9e70d8e3","tid":2198262,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T09:05:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C1lvSjaLXgc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC1lvSjaLXgc&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=dafd2f7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C1lvSjaLXgc</a><br />\n以歸納法推論出嘅結論並非必然，但係就係當下最可靠嘅說法"},{"pid":"12a5d85427c32e933ec4524b0f9dcc9beab7e7be","tid":2198262,"uid":88663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14894509cefd560ed907a5630815eadee15559bc","tid":2198262,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:44:36.000Z","msg":"唔得閒睇片<br />\n樓主可唔可以簡單總結吓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:01:40.000Z","msg":"首先，科學知識同科學方法可以係獨立嘅兩樣野，任何現象都可以以科學方法去研究，包括中醫。點解？因為科學方法係一種態度，嚴謹求真嘅精神<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而上面啲片係講，可靠嘅理論/講法係有五個半準：<br />\n1驗證性<br />\n<br />\n2否證性<br />\n<br />\n3重複聲<br />\n<br />\n4預測性<br />\n<br />\n5簡單性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果我哋要得出遵從醫生準則嘅理論知識知識，就要依照下列程序：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1觀察<br />\n<br />\n2發問<br />\n<br />\n3假設<br />\n<br />\n4實驗<br />\n<br />\n5結論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果當根據假設所作出嘅預測同實驗結果不符（無論個實，<br />\n驗係你自己做定人哋做），就在表個假設係錯嘅，要重新<br />\n<br />\n建立一啲新嘅價錢，直到預測同實驗結果吻合，咁就會得<br />\n<br />\n出一個新嘅，相當可靠嘅理論/知識/講法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正"},{"pid":"2155245ad1797ffb1b1e0c06bedaa888f76e5622","tid":2198262,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"15366050d338ab0d7f2f549044522fe7885c3cdd","tid":2198262,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:57:39.000Z","msg":"關於哲學-科學的隨筆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2051839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2051839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2efa78c03d9c688eede6ef379e44795f9ddc2a9a","tid":2198262,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15366050d338ab0d7f2f549044522fe7885c3cdd","tid":2198262,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:57:39.000Z","msg":"關於哲學-科學的隨筆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2051839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2051839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T11:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb263d11075e0ac9f7ed116b6c44a114d97e090","tid":2198262,"uid":362366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"親身先試下科學方法避孕，然後試下非科學方法避孕，應該就感受到科學方法嘅重要性<br />\n<br />\n另亦盡量鼓吹所有相似年齡及健康狀況嘅人都同樣咁做並匯報結果，提升統計學上嘅重要性<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">利申：唔識</span>"},{"pid":"5327f13f532216cfd761e9967d3d0422ebcfc1ad","tid":2198262,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfb263d11075e0ac9f7ed116b6c44a114d97e090","tid":2198262,"uid":362366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"親身先試下科學方法避孕，然後試下非科學方法避孕，應該就感受到科學方法嘅重要性<br />\n<br />\n另亦盡量鼓吹所有相似年齡及健康狀況嘅人都同樣咁做並匯報結果，提升統計學上嘅重要性<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">利申：唔識</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"你同我講嘅科學方法根本係兩樣野<br />\n<br />\n你講嘅係用科學知識去解決某啲問題<br />\n<br />\n我講嘅係研究事物嘅態度（嚴謹求真）"},{"pid":"3d2de9e08882327a8a2527ee59153d06b2c89887","tid":2198262,"uid":362366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5327f13f532216cfd761e9967d3d0422ebcfc1ad","tid":2198262,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfb263d11075e0ac9f7ed116b6c44a114d97e090","tid":2198262,"uid":362366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"親身先試下科學方法避孕，然後試下非科學方法避孕，應該就感受到科學方法嘅重要性<br />\n<br />\n另亦盡量鼓吹所有相似年齡及健康狀況嘅人都同樣咁做並匯報結果，提升統計學上嘅重要性<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">利申：唔識</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"你同我講嘅科學方法根本係兩樣野<br />\n<br />\n你講嘅係用科學知識去解決某啲問題<br />\n<br />\n我講嘅係研究事物嘅態度（嚴謹求真）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"神農嘗百草都嚴謹求真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce59722876e1b56a54c59a218a079e2f082f49a4","tid":2198262,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d2de9e08882327a8a2527ee59153d06b2c89887","tid":2198262,"uid":362366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco